quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  22,47,"Hi…ìe …óa…ì…ìire yaccinaneede Lepte …óen, [e …óum le] Alla lunndataako fodoore Makko nden. Pellet √±allal ka Joomi maa…óa ko wano duu…ìi wuluure no limorton non"
  22,48,"No foti heewde e saare nde Mi nennani …óum hara kayre ko nde too√±unde, refti Mi nannginde ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde nden"
  22,49,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, anndee min ko mi jertinoowo on …ìanngu…óo"
  22,50,∆Åen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin no woodani …ìe haforanal e arsike teddu…óo
  22,51,"∆Åen yaccii…ìe [fii bonnugol] e Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìe ronkinaa [Men] ko …ìen …óon woni yim…ìe Jahiimaawe ngen"
  22,52,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa immorde e Nulaa…óo wanaa kadi Annabaajo si wanaa si o janngii Seytaane werloto e nder janki makko kin. Alla itta ko Seytaane werlii kon, refti Alla tabintina Aayeeje Makko …óen. Alla ko O Anndu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  22,53,"Fii yo O wa…óu ko Seytaane werlotoo ko njarraboye wonannde …ìen …ìe nawnaare woni ka …ìer…óe mu'un e …ìe …ìer…óe mu'un yoori …ìen. Pellet, too√±oo…ìe …ìen …ìe wonii e lurral wo…ó…óungal"
  22,54,"Fii yo …ìen okkaa…ìe Ganndal ngal anndu pellet, ko [Alqur'aanaare nden woni] Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi maa…óa …ìe gom…óina nde, …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yankinanoo …óum. Pellet Alla Fewnay …ìen gom…óin…ìe faade e Laawol Focciingol"
  22,55,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe seerataa hi…ìe e nder sikke [fii Alqur'aana] haa Darngal ngal ara e ma…ì…ìe e juhayee maa…óum ara e ma…ì…ìe Lepte √ëalaande sa…ótunde"
